<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wrestle" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wrestle,</orth> to contend who shall throw the other down: <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 99</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 99</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 99</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> 133 <cit><quote>(with).</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.244" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 244</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.194" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 194</bibl>. Metaphorically: <cit><quote>w. with affection,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 42</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 21</bibl>. <cit><quote>great affections --ing in thy bosom,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 2, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I'll w. with you in my strength of love,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 2, 62</bibl></cit>.
